.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, iced-tea, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, quad-bike, trike
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the person drinking cola is not the person driving the trike##6
2. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person driving the train##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person drinking fanta##7
5. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person driving the train is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | cola | iced-tea | lemonade |
| Transport   | trike | quad-bike  | snowmobile  | train    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

