.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, librarian, musician, photographer
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, goldfish
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, snooker, backgammon
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
2. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the goat##2
4. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
5. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the musician is somewhere between the person playing snooker and the person playing whist##7
8. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
| Job         | librarian | musician | doctor    | photographer |
| Pet         | frog      | goldfish | dog       | goat         |
| Game   | snooker | backgammon    | scrabble | whist     |

