 1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching crime movies##2
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the person watching adventure movies is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | sprite     | fanta      | milk     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | adventure   | comedy   | crime |
| Transport     | tram     | helicopter | skateboard | roller   |

