5. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
8. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who likes fuchsia##6

